{"type": "article", "id": 22444, "title": "最简化家具组", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-18T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122229MPJSVzv0dToNuIHg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">丹麦家具品牌 fredericia 和英国设计师Jasper Morrison 合作了这组家具，包括边桌、沙发和餐桌。他们想要去除所有装饰和不必要的细节，家具都保留的基本形态。其中绿色的沙发靠背和扶手从侧面看是垂直的，但内侧是柔和的弧形，沙发扶手从靠背向外逐渐变窄，似乎连成一体，非常优雅大方。而几款圆形边桌有多种型号选择，可以随意组合或单独使用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122226fVcvTkqpLnh7zrX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122227xgJ3kiBwnUM2bcZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55623472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122227qPMmYVn32BcThIW7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65647922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122227wRSrVFe7qxo18a3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63325183\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122228VaEAOpcieX5ISMND.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}